┌─────────────────────┐
│ INSTALL FILE (v0.1) │
│ femto blog system   │
│ version 0.1         │
└─────────────────────┘

(Note that these steps will be obsolete as soon as the install wizard 
 is available.)

══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

femto can be installed easily with 3 steps.


▶▶▶ 1) Prepare Database
Shipped with this file you find the database install script depending
on your database system. Run it in your database administration tool
(e.g. mysql-admin, phpmyadmin).
⚠ Note that the first line tries to create a new database ("femto").
  You can disable that line by commenting it but remember to adjust
  the DBNAME setting in the settings file (see below).
⚠ The last part concerns user privileges. In its default configuration
  femto uses two different users for accessing the database in viewing
  mode (your visitors) and editing mode (in the admin panel). These
  are created and supplied with proper privileges at the script’s end.
  As many shared hosters deny the creation of users, this commands are
  disabled. It is recommended to enable them.


▶▶▶ 2) Edit Settings
Most settings can be set in the file .settings/settings.php. Also, 
this is where you set the database password.
Please consult the help URL for a detailed description.
⚠ Feel free to adjust the translations for your language(s). You will
  find them in the locale directory. English and German are included
  by default; English is the default language set in the settings.php.
⚠ Maybe you need to adapt the locale setting to fit your system’s
  locale.
⚠ Do not overlook the .htaccess file. You may want to set review the
  cache control settings.
⚠ Same thing for robots.txt. You can edit sitemap URL there.
⚠ If you use nginx instead of Apache, please add the content of
  nginx.conf to your server directive in your configuration file.


▶▶▶ 3) Log into the Admin Panel
Visit /admin/ and use admin as the temporary username and password to
login. It is highly recommended to change or replace this account as
soon as possible.
You can start blogging now.


 Enjoy femto!

 Regards,
   Eduard Dopler


